  <h1>Simulation 03<br><span class="sim-subtitle">Search &amp; Filter</span></h1>
  <p>
    Live search and filter over a dataset. Demonstrates how <code>model</code> wires input to a signal,
    and <code>computed</code> derives the filtered list — with zero manual DOM manipulation.
  </p>
